# Polkadot
⚠️⚠️⚠️ Polkadot provides the llm compatible docs!!! ⚠️⚠️⚠️

Use this link if you are low on credits: `https://docs.polkadot.com/llms.txt`

Otherwise use this: `https://docs.polkadot.com/llms-full.txt`


## Usage with Cursor ai
1. Go to the Cursor chat and click on `@/Docs/+ Add new doc`
2. Paste this URL: `https://docs.polkadot.com/llms-full.txt`
3. Name it `polkadot-docs`
